      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LET'S CAUSE KAOS (8) failed to feature last start after drifting back at Sandown, but prior to that won comfortably by 5.5 lengths at this track (25.78) beating Did Not in a Grade 5 on March 17. Can discover winning form. SUPER BATMAN (2) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 6 lengths (25.84) at this track. Looks suited and has winning claims again. NORBIT (1) finds it hard to break through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when second (25.64) at Ballarat. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SHADE OF PALE (7) showed great speed to lead all the way last start. Big chance again.",
